snippet.title: Empire of Atlantis PS2 Gameplay ( Phoenix Games ) Playstation 2
snippet.description:
Heres a quick video showing the various modes to choose on the Phoenix Games activity game called The Empire of Atlantis.
Just like many other of Phoenix Games releases, this one is just another rehash of games like Animal Soccer World and Cartoon Kingdom.

Please check out my other videos for more Phoenix Games PS2 releases
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNZylG5ZROX7uhBo-GjnHqg
